data.description: ** Seller willing to pay up to $5000 toward closing costs. Welcome to this well-maintained home in the desirable Liberty Park neighborhood of Clarksville, TN. This charming house features 3 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms and 1.5 car garage, providing ample space for comfortable living. Step outside onto the wood deck, perfect for  hosting gatherings with friends and family. The interior has been freshly painted, giving the home a clean and modern feel. Additionally, new flooring has been installed throughout. The fenced yard offers privacy and security, making it an ideal space for pets or outdoor activities. The bonus room provides flexibility, allowing you to create a home office, playroom, or additional living space to suit your needs. Convenient location to Fort Campbell and LBL.
